---
title: Barbecue Chicken Sarnie with Dressed Baby Gem and Sweet Potato Fries
description: Looking for a tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Barbecue Chicken Sarnie in just 20 minutes for a balanced and tasty dinnertime.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/barbecue-chicken-sarnie-bc224a0a-e66bbee7.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/barbecue-chicken-sarnie-5e0f64ecbe44d328aa3b7e3e-be084058.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/barbecue-chicken-sarnie-5e0f64ecbe44d328aa3b7e3e
author: Mimi Morley
course: main course
time required: 20 minutes
servings: 2
cuisine: American
